<h2>bcrm: Bayesian Continual Reassessment Method for Phase I
Dose-Escalation Trials</h2>
<p>Implements a wide variety of one- and two-parameter Bayesian CRM
    designs. The program can run interactively, allowing the user to enter outcomes
    after each cohort has been recruited, or via simulation to assess operating
    characteristics. See Sweeting et al. (2013): &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.18637%2Fjss.v054.i13">doi:10.18637/jss.v054.i13</a>&gt;.</p>
